snippet.title: Let's Play Farmer's Daughter Valentine's Day Special
snippet.description:
It's February 14th:  Have you gotten laid today?  I have, and it was on the C64!  Come watch the cyber maddening tale of our epic lightning rod salesman protagonist and his EPIC quest to score with a girl that's basically the stereotypical equivalent of jailbait in such places as Arkansas or possibly even Texas... although I haven't seen any examples of such myself.

Just as well.  My ass would get handed around in prison like a fat, floppy frisbee.
